Labels.Notes: #WMprotein20x - protein per gram tissue in 20x homogenates. These homogenates were used to measure all liver enzymes and white muscle COX, CS, MDH, CPK, PGI, PFK, TPI, ALD, GAPDH, PK, LDH

# EnzymeAbbreviation.liv - activity per gram tissue in liver
# EnzymeAbbreviation.wm.prot - activity per mg protein in white muscle
# EnzymeAbbreviation.liv.prot - activity per mg protein in liver
# per.red.muscle - percentage red muscle measured in muscle steak
